title: Michael Nonbo
text: Michael Nonbo (16 November 1973) is a <a href="Denmark">Danish</a> former professional <a href="association%20football">football</a> player, who played 355 games and scored 14 goals in the <a href="Danish%20Superliga">Danish Superliga</a> from 1991 to 2006, representing <a href="N%C3%A6stved%20IF">Næstved IF</a>, <a href="Aarhus%20Gymnastikforening">AGF</a>, <a href="Viborg%20FF">Viborg FF</a>, and <a href="S%C3%B8nderjyskE%20Fodbold">SønderjyskE</a>. He played 16 games and scored three goals for the <a href="Denmark%20national%20under-21%20football%20team">Denmark national under-21 football team</a> from November 1993 to October 1995.
